Abstract: The bride teaches kindergarten. The bridegroom is a lawyer.
Snippet: The bride teaches kindergarten. The bridegroom is a lawyer.
LeadParagraph: Holly Helen Slimak, a daughter of Theresa J. Linger and Sheldon L. Linger of Gloucester, Va., is to be married Sunday to Christopher Stuart Colby, the son of Janet Colby and W. Stuart Colby of Ossining, N.Y. The Rev. Robert Michael Dunn, a Roman Catholic priest, is to perform the ceremony at St. Bernard Catholic Church in Holmes Beach, Fla.
